headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Expeditors International of Washington (EXPD) After Its Strong 1-Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Expeditors International of Washington is still good value after a strong run, this article walks through what the current price might be implying. The stock last closed at US$162.41, with returns of 2.2% over 7 days, 8.5% over 30 days, 6.9% year to date, 49.0% over 1 year and 57.7% over 3 years. It is therefore worth asking what expectations are now built into the share price. Recent moves in the shares have come alongside ongoing attention on global freight and...
